&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;This is an exciting opportunity to help build the Strategic Finance &amp;amp; Business Operations function at a high growth, pre-IPO company. &amp;nbsp;You will play a critical role partnering cross-functionally as a trusted advisor to various teams to drive business insights, decision-making rigor, and operational excellence, and help Verkada reach the next level of scale and operating sophistication in the process. We seek talented generalists who can engage at the most senior levels while still sweating the details.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
