&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Roundtrip flights to and from our San Mateo HQ&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Daily lunch, complimentary barista-made drinks, and fully stocked snacks to keep you fueled&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Intern-exclusive events and mixers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
