&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Time off to rest and recharge through personal sick time and volunteer time off to support causes you care about&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Additional Information&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;You must be independently authorized to work in the U.S. We are unable to sponsor or take over sponsorship of an employment visa for this role, at this time&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
