&lt;li&gt;Provide guidance on complex employee relations matters, investigations, ensuring fair, consistent, and legally sound resolutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive cross-company programs to benefit our entire employee base.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
